---
---

<section id="offerings" class="engagements">
	<div class="container">

		<header class="eng-header reveal">
			<p class="section-label">THE ENGAGEMENTS</p>
			<h2 class="eng-h2">Built for where you are.</h2>
		</header>

		<div class="engagement-list">

			<!-- 01 ─── Founder Storytelling -->
			<div class="engagement-row">
				<div class="row-index">
					<span class="row-num">01</span>
				</div>
				<div class="row-body">
					<div class="row-title-line">
						<h3 class="eng-name">Founder Storytelling</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="eng-desc">
						You know what you're building. Getting the market to believe it is a different problem.
						We find the version of your story that's impossible to copy, then put it in the rooms
						that change outcomes.
					</p>
					<ul class="eng-outputs">
						<li>Founder story ready for investors, press, recruiting, and customers</li>
						<li>Channel strategy built around where your buyers actually pay attention</li>
					</ul>
					<a href="#contact" class="eng-link">Start Story →</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- 02 ─── Positioning Sprint -->
			<div class="engagement-row">
				<div class="row-index">
					<span class="row-num">02</span>
				</div>
				<div class="row-body">
					<div class="row-title-line">
						<h3 class="eng-name">Positioning Sprint</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="eng-desc">
						You're losing deals you should be winning. Usually it's not the product.
						We interview your customers and your losses, then build positioning
						from the evidence up.
					</p>
					<ul class="eng-outputs">
						<li>Positioning deck built from customer interviews and win/loss data</li>
						<li>First call deck that closes the gap between interest and next meeting</li>
						<li>Homepage blueprint that converts the right visitors</li>
					</ul>
					<a href="#contact" class="eng-link">Start Positioning →</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- 03 ─── The Growth Protocol -->
			<div class="engagement-row">
				<div class="row-index">
					<span class="row-num">03</span>
				</div>
				<div class="row-body">
					<div class="row-title-line">
						<h3 class="eng-name">The Growth Protocol</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="eng-desc">
						Growth is slower than the board expects and you know something is blocking it.
						We find it, name it, and build the 90-day plan around the moves that will
						actually change the number.
					</p>
					<ul class="eng-outputs">
						<li>Diagnostic memo showing exactly where deals stall and why</li>
						<li>90-day roadmap with three to five prioritized moves</li>
						<li>Your next hire identified by the bottleneck it solves</li>
					</ul>
					<a href="#contact" class="eng-link">Start Protocol →</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- 04 ─── Marketing Systems -->
			<div class="engagement-row">
				<div class="row-index">
					<span class="row-num">04</span>
				</div>
				<div class="row-body">
					<div class="row-title-line">
						<h3 class="eng-name">Marketing Systems</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="eng-desc">
						Your team spends most of their time on execution and not enough on the work
						that moves the number. We build the systems that change that ratio.
					</p>
					<ul class="eng-outputs">
						<li>Custom workflows built around your team's actual workload</li>
						<li>A clear framework for where systems run and where your team leads</li>
						<li>Onboarding that drives real adoption, not shelf life</li>
					</ul>
					<a href="#contact" class="eng-link">Start Systems →</a>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
	</div>
</section>


<style>
	.engagements {
		background: var(--white);
		padding: 7rem 0 8rem;
	}

	/* ── Section header ───────────────────────── */
	.eng-header {
		margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
	}

	.section-label {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.28em;
		color: var(--orange);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.eng-h2 {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-weight: 900;
		font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 4.5vw, 4rem);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		line-height: 0.95;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--black);
	}

	/* ── Engagement list ──────────────────────── */
	.engagement-list {
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(25, 21, 20, 0.12);
	}

	.engagement-row {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr;
		gap: 0 3.5rem;
		padding: 3.5rem 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(25, 21, 20, 0.12);
		align-items: start;
		opacity: 0;
		transition: opacity 0.6s ease;
	}

	.engagement-row.active {
		opacity: 1;
	}

	/* Row number */
	.row-index {
		padding-top: 0.3rem;
	}

	.row-num {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-weight: 900;
		font-size: 2.8rem;
		line-height: 1;
		color: rgba(25, 21, 20, 0.1);
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
		display: block;
		transition: color 0.3s;
	}

	.engagement-row:hover .row-num {
		color: rgba(255, 84, 2, 0.3);
	}

	/* Row content */
	.row-title-line {
		display: flex;
		align-items: baseline;
		gap: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.eng-name {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.5vw, 2.1rem);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
		line-height: 1;
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--black);
	}

	.eng-desc {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		color: rgba(25, 21, 20, 0.6);
		line-height: 1.7;
		max-width: 580px;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	/* Output list — clean, no label */
	.eng-outputs {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0 0 2rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.4rem;
	}

	.eng-outputs li {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		color: rgba(25, 21, 20, 0.45);
		line-height: 1.6;
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 1rem;
	}

	.eng-outputs li::before {
		content: "–";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--orange);
		opacity: 0.6;
	}

	/* CTA link */
	.eng-link {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.18em;
		color: var(--black);
		text-decoration: none;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 84, 2, 0.45);
		padding-bottom: 2px;
		display: inline-block;
		transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
	}
	.eng-link:hover {
		color: var(--orange);
		border-color: var(--orange);
	}

	/* ── Responsive ───────────────────────────── */
	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.engagement-row {
			grid-template-columns: 70px 1fr;
			gap: 0 2rem;
		}
		.row-num { font-size: 2rem; }
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.engagements { padding: 5rem 0 6rem; }
		.engagement-row {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1.5rem;
			padding: 2.5rem 0;
		}
		.row-num { font-size: 1.5rem; }
	}
</style>
